<header class='post-header title-container fix'>
	<div class="title">
		<h1 class="posttitle"><a href='http://btcgeek.com/bitshares-guide/' class='entry-title' rel='bookmark' title='Bitshares: A Comprehensive Guide' >Bitshares: A Comprehensive Guide</a></h1>
		<div class="postdata fix">
					<span class="category"><span class="icon">&nbsp;</span><a href="http://btcgeek.com/category/alternate-cryptocurrencies/" title="View all posts in Alternate Cryptocurrencies" rel="category tag">Alternate Cryptocurrencies</a></span>
